## Status

`{{.StatusPath}}` is master-written. The framework does not populate it. Write it as JSON whenever run state materially changes:
```json
{"phase":"working|complete","required_remaining":0,"open_required_ids":["req-1"],"active_sessions":["session-N"],"keep_session":"session-N","last_verified_at":"2026-03-26T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-03-26T00:00:00Z"}
```
Set `keep_session` when a develop-mode session should be merged before stopping. Keep this file factual: progress coverage, active ownership, and latest verification timestamps belong here; verdicts belong in journals, proof, and summary.
